%% FMS Guardrails Orchestrator - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Client Application
    participant Orch as Orchestrator<br/>8033/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant Health as Health Server<br/>8034/TCP HTTP
    participant Chunker as Chunker Service<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    participant Detector as Detector Service(s)<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant TGIS as TGIS Generation<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    participant vLLM as vLLM / OpenAI<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    participant OTel as OTLP Collector<br/>4317/4318 TCP

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 1: Unary Classification with Text Generation (v1 API)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v1/task/classification-with-text-generation<br/>TLS 1.2+ (optional), Header passthrough
    Orch->>Chunker: Chunk input text<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, TLS/mTLS, Client certs
    Chunker-->>Orch: Text chunks
    Orch->>Detector: Analyze input chunks<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, TLS/mTLS, Client certs
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results (input)
    Orch->>TGIS: Generate text (Generate RPC)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, TLS/mTLS, Client certs
    TGIS-->>Orch: Generated text
    Orch->>Chunker: Chunk output text<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, TLS/mTLS
    Chunker-->>Orch: Output chunks
    Orch->>Detector: Analyze output chunks<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, TLS/mTLS
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results (output)
    Orch-->>Client: Classification + Generation response<br/>JSON, TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 2: Chat Completions with Detection (v2 API, OpenAI-compatible)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/chat/completions-detection<br/>TLS 1.2+ (optional), Header passthrough
    Orch->>vLLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, TLS, Bearer token (forwarded)
    vLLM-->>Orch: Chat completion response
    Orch->>Detector: Analyze generated content<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, TLS/mTLS
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results
    Orch-->>Client: Completions + Detection response<br/>SSE or JSON, TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,OTel: Flow 3: Streaming Content Detection (v2 API)
    Client->>Orch: POST /api/v2/text/detection/stream-content<br/>NDJSON, TLS 1.2+ (optional)
    Orch->>Chunker: Stream chunks (BidiStreaming)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2, TLS/mTLS
    Chunker-->>Orch: Chunked text stream
    Orch->>Detector: Analyze chunks<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, TLS/mTLS
    Detector-->>Orch: Detection results (streaming)
    Orch-->>Client: Detection results stream<br/>NDJSON, TLS 1.2+

    Note over Health,OTel: Health & Observability
    Client->>Health: GET /health<br/>HTTP 8034/TCP, No auth
    Health-->>Client: Health status
    Orch->>OTel: Export traces & metrics<br/>OTLP gRPC/HTTP
